item.description:
We have had many click and shoots this summer, so it's time to show off your favorite photo for them!

Kelby Walk, Art in the Park, Trash the Dress, Tornadoes Game.... just to name a few!

Have not been to click and shoot yet? That's ok- just bring something from a summer time shoot!

So pick it, print it and bring it!



Donna and Scott
